data.description: Back On Market!!!  Welcome to Williams Street! 3 bed 1.5 bath colonial is waiting for YOU! Enter from the composite stairs into the large, bright living room. Slider from the formal dining room overlooks the large backyard. Stylish, durable wood laminate flooring throughout the first floor. Spacious eat in kitchen boasts bay window, beamed ceiling and island. Separate 1st floor laundry and convenient half bath complete the first level. New HW stair treads lead you upstairs to find 3 large bedrooms and a full bath with granite vanity top. Private, fenced in backyard on level lot features patio area and composite deck.  Quiet dead end street. Walking distance to Nashua River Rail Trail. Storage Shed. New bulkhead and radon system. New stair treads. Don't miss your chance to call this house "home"!
